Package com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.documents.types Description

Provides interfaces specifying the types of documents available in Geneious. Document types dealing specifically with sequences are instead specified in the com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.documents.sequence package.

For default implementations of the interfaces defined in this pacakage, see the com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.implementations package.
